title: Jessa Duggar Compares First and Second Pregnancies With Side-by-Side Baby Bump Pics
text:
PHOTOS: Jessa Duggar and Ben Seewald's Sweetest Instagram Shots 
The 19 Kids and Counting alum announced she and Ben, 21, were expecting their second bundle of joy last August. "We are overjoyed to announce that Spurgeon has a new title in life as big brother!" the couple, who wed in November 2014, told Us Weekly . "We are so thankful that God is adding to our family â€” 2017 is shaping up to be a wonderful year already and we know Spurgeon will do a great job in his new role. Having Spurgeon has been such a wonderful blessing and we cannot wait to see the face of this sweet new baby." PHOTOS: Jill Duggar and Derick Dillard's Wedding Album 
Last week, Duggar celebrated her baby shower with about 130 of her closest friends and family members, as Us Weekly exclusively reported. She chose to forgo gifts, but received a surprise date-night basket to enjoy with her husband.
